      "## 2. Shopify POS",
      "**Best for:** Retailers who already sell online through Shopify and want a unified online-offline system.\n\nShopify POS is the natural extension of the Shopify ecommerce platform. If your business is primarily online and you are adding a physical store, Shopify POS gives you a single inventory pool across channels.\n\n**Key features:** Unified online and in-store inventory, integrated payments, customer profiles with cross-channel purchase history, staff management, and hardware options.\n\n**Pricing:** POS Lite is included with all Shopify plans (from $39/month). POS Pro is $89/month per location.\n\n**Pros:** Excellent omnichannel experience, large app ecosystem, clean interface.\n\n**Cons:** GST compliance requires third-party apps. No IMEI tracking. Pricing in USD adds exchange rate variability for Indian businesses.",
      "## 3. Lightspeed Retail",
